features: 【Charging function with USB Ports】The nightstand is arranged with 2 AC and 2 USB socket. One of USB ports is designed for the led lights, the AC socket and the other USB socket provide convenience for charging your phone, earphone, desk lamp, and other small electrical appliances.

It will look more beautiful when the light is in the dark. The beautiful LED light will make your home looks more modern and fashionable.

【Sturdy & Durable】Bedside table is made of premium particle board and metal material which is thick and durable enough to strongly support the end table itself and stuff inside or on it. Overall dimension: 16.54" (L) x 15.75" (W) x 33.86" (H). The tabletop has maximum weighted capacity of 33 LBS.

【Sufficient Storage Space】The night stand complete with 1 drawer, middle shelf, and 1 bottom shelf for additional storage, so your alarm clocks, table lamps, magazines, books, and even skin care products can be stored well. The top small shelf is designed for simple storage, placing glasses, small items or your cell phone that is charging.

【Easy Assemble & Customer Service】All labeled pieces, tools and step-by-step installation manual are included in the package, which you can easily assemble this end tables for living room individually. We provide 24 hours customer service to help you with any questions or concerns you may have.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Bit Smaller than I Anticipated
reviews.reviewText: It's about 80% the size of my previous nightstand, so I had to make some adjustments to what I wanted to put in the drawer and underneath.However it holds my tablets and phone nicely with room for my prescription bottles on top. These were the most important features for me so I am generally happy.The drawer works smoothly, but the bottom is very thin. So don't put anything heavy in it.The led lights are nice, but have one major downside. There is no way to turn them off without unplugging them or throwing the switch for the entire power strip.The app works on my phone just fine. The music option makes for fun party lights, but they only go fast. So if you have slow music they don't match. But fast music is a lot of fun! You can adjust just about everything from the app, color, brightness, changing speed. You just can't turn the led lights off.It goes together fairly easily in a couple hours and seems solid once built. The drawer glides smoothly and easily. The wood laminate is a very nice color and has no damage. I give it 5 stars for quality of materials!If the nightstand had been a bit bigger, the drawer bottom a bit thicker, and there was a switch to turn off the lights on the app and nightstand I would rate it overall 5 stars.As it is, it is a very nice little nightstand and I look forward to using it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy nightstand that holds quite a bit!
reviews.reviewText: I wanted a new nightstand that I could organize a bit better than what I previously used as a nightstand. And since I wanted a new one, the man got a new one too :)Assembly: Pretty straight forward as long as you follow along with the instructions. I did notice a few typos (for example, it will show that you need 5 of a type of screw, but in the zoomed in picture, it will say 4. Easiest way around this is to just count them in the zoomed out picture.) There was also an issue with holes properly lining up in subsequent steps if you tightened the bolts down all the way in a previous step. Luckily it was easy enough to loosen them back up, align things properly, install the hardware for the step you’re on, and then retighten. There’s also one locknut that you won’t be able to reach with a screwdriver—the larger of the included Allen wrenches will do the trick for that one though (that’s not stated in the instructions—the instructions show using a screwdriver which is impossible.) Took a little over an hour to assemble one.Seems quite sturdy and I’ve loaded mine down with books (all titles I recommend if you happen to be able to read them in the picture.) The only real downside I’ve noticed is that the drawer depth isn’t deep enough to fit a standard size notebook into vertically, you have to place them in horizontally. To be fair though, if I would’ve actually broke out a tape measure and checked things out beforehand, I would’ve known this. It’s a minor thing, but did surprise me that a standard notebook couldn’t fit in that way. Perhaps the manufacturers will make the overall structure a bit deeper in the future. As for the rest of the size—I did break out a tape measure before ordering, so overall, it met my expectations as far as the overall size. Not too big, not too small. The hooks are a handy feature and I may even get more to be able to hang additional items. Currently, one holds my sunglasses and the other holds a bag and a clipboard. The lights are a nice touch…pretty basic, nothing fancy…but frees up space by not needing to put a lamp on the nightstand.Overall, very pleased with the ease of assembly, sturdiness, and how much it holds. My kids want them now too, so I see purchasing these again in the future. Price point is fair for what they are and what they’re made of.

reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Night stand is to small and low quality control
reviews.reviewText: The night stand is just to small. It almost feels like it's for a kids room. I do like the raised edges, because I tend to have alot of stuff on my stand and don't want it to fall off. However I ended up not using the light in the long run and I wish there were bigger night stands on the market.When I first got this and tried putting it together, the holes did not align correctly and had to contact customer care. They had to manufacture me new parts and it took a while.BEWARE, this is not an Amazon supplier. If you don't like it, you'll need to pay for the shipping to send it back which will literally cost the same amount you paid for this
